frama-c - готов:
frama-c -eva -cpp-command "gcc -E -I/path/to/includes -DINT_MAX=2147483647" source.c

splint - готов:
splint -I/path/to/includes -DINT_MAX=2147483647 source.c

infer - готов:
infer run -- gcc -c path/to/source.c \
-I /path/to/includes \
-DINT_MAX=2147483647


clang-tidy - готов:
clang-tidy source.c -- -I/path/to/includes -DINT_MAX=2147483647

Clang Static Analyzer (scan-build) - готов:
scan-build --use-analyzer=clang --keep-cc \
-I /path/to/includes \
-DINT_MAX=2147483647 \
make

cppcheck - готов:
cppcheck --enable=all --inconclusive --force \
-I /path/to/includes \
-DINT_MAX=2147483647 \
-DSIZE_MAX=18446744073709551615 \
path/to/source

Flawfinder - готов:
flawfinder --columns --minlevel=1 source.c

sparse - готов:
sparse -I/path/to/includes -DINT_MAX=2147483647 source.c

RATS - готов:
rats -w 3 -c source.c


